5. Qc1) (32. Qb4 $16) 32... Qg5 { [%clk 0:01:04] } 33. h4! { [%clk 0:00:43] } 33... Qxh4! { [%clk 0:00:52] } 34. Rh1 { [%clk 0:00:42] } 34... Bf1+!! { I missed this move in my calculations. } { [%clk 0:00:49] } (34... Qxh1+ 35. Kxh1 fxe5 36. dxe5 $18) 35. Kg1? { [%clk 0:00:40] } (35. Rxf1 fxe5 36. Qe2 { was still good enough for equality, but with little time on the clock it would have been tough anyway. }) 35... Bh3! $19 { 0-1 White resigns. } { I missed this move as well. (Everything else loses, but 35...Bh3! wins.) White cannot parry the check on a1 and save his knight at the same time. } { [%clk 0:00:48] } 0-1


